00:37:01,649 --> 00:37:06,491
Because in exchange, we give them free keys.

675
00:37:06,491 --> 00:37:08,252
Some of them just do it for free.

676
00:37:13,576 --> 00:37:16,118
Some of them just do it because they're passionate about the game.

677
00:37:16,118 --> 00:37:24,164
So you can see it's just a dump of documentation.

678
00:37:24,164 --> 00:37:27,506
We have charts here. If it's in red, the page doesn't exist yet.

679
00:37:27,506 --> 00:37:29,608
If it's in blue, then the page does exist.

680
00:37:29,608 --> 00:37:33,150
And so some of it is in an English template.

681
00:37:33,150 --> 00:37:37,434
You can see it's still in English, even though this is the Chinese page.

682
00:37:37,434 --> 00:37:43,078
But you can see people are slowly editing section by section about the game.

683
00:37:43,893 --> 00:37:48,094
So localization is a big project.

684
00:37:48,094 --> 00:37:50,815
And you don't have to have it in game right at the beginning.

685
00:37:50,815 --> 00:37:53,956
What you can do is, while you're programming,

686
00:37:53,956 --> 00:37:57,276
you can ask the community to help you localize.

687
00:37:57,276 --> 00:37:59,997
So when we do localize, everything is here.

688
00:37:59,997 --> 00:38:02,778
And what are they working for?

689
00:38:02,778 --> 00:38:06,419
You can give them game keys I mentioned earlier.

690
00:38:06,419 --> 00:38:10,040
You can give them titles if you use Discord, or even in game.

691
00:38:10,040 --> 00:38:11,900
You can give them something special.

692
00:38:12,551 --> 00:38:15,152
In Discord, it takes two seconds to add them a title,

693
00:38:15,152 --> 00:38:16,472
but they're stoked about it.

694
00:38:16,472 --> 00:38:21,053
We give them a secret channel called Wikia Masters.

695
00:38:21,053 --> 00:38:26,734
And so only the Wikia people that contribute and localize

696
00:38:26,734 --> 00:38:28,795
can see this channel in Discord.

697
00:38:28,795 --> 00:38:30,415
It's huge for morale.

698
00:38:30,415 --> 00:38:34,336
They think it's super cool, and they're part of the community.

699
00:38:34,336 --> 00:38:35,176
They're engaged.

700
00:38:35,176 --> 00:38:37,757
And sometimes they compete to see

701
00:38:37,757 --> 00:38:42,438
who has the highest edit counts, which is a win-win, you know?

702
00:38:43,283 --> 00:38:44,164
It's a wonderful thing.

703
00:38:44,164 --> 00:38:47,705
And so we actually have quite a lot of translations.

704
00:38:47,705 --> 00:38:51,586
The only thing we did was the English one.

705
00:38:51,586 --> 00:38:54,127
But even then, the community will help expand it,

706
00:38:54,127 --> 00:38:56,087
because they're very passionate.

