00:38:56,087 --> 00:38:58,268
If you get a community to follow you,

708
00:38:58,268 --> 00:39:01,609
Discord again is the key to that.

709
00:39:01,609 --> 00:39:04,350
And Discourse, that forum I mentioned earlier.

