00:39:04,350 --> 00:39:07,251
Then these people will help you do this for free,

711
00:39:07,251 --> 00:39:11,192
because they want their community to understand

712
00:39:11,192 --> 00:39:12,532
the game in their own language.

713
00:39:13,500 --> 00:39:18,302
We have some people who are very passionate, and they just want to translate.

