00:40:05,189 --> 00:40:06,710
Maybe it will be good one day.

731
00:40:06,710 --> 00:40:07,410
Maybe.

732
00:40:07,410 --> 00:40:10,131
But for now, just simply skip it.

733
00:40:10,131 --> 00:40:11,012
As for PlayFab.

